{"word":"Bashan","slug":"bashan","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bashan</b> <a href=\"#/H1316\">H1316</a> <br/> A region east of the Jordan and north of Arnon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=5'>Gen 14:5</a><br/> Og, king of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=12'>Jos 13:12</a><br/> Allotted to the two and one half tribes, which had their possession east of the Jordan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=33'>Num 32:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=14'>Deu 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=6'>Jos 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=31'>Jos 13:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=1'>Jos 17:1</a><br/> Invaded and taken by Hazael, king of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=33'>2Ki 10:33</a><br/> Retaken by Jehoash<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=25'>2Ki 13:25</a><br/> Fertility and productiveness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=33&verse=9'>Isa 33:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=19'>Jer 50:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=1&verse=4'>Nah 1:4</a><br/> Forests of, famous<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=13'>Isa 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=6'>Eze 27:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=11&verse=2'>Zec 11:2</a><br/> Distinguished for its fine cattle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=14'>Deu 32:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=22&verse=12'>Psa 22:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=39&verse=18'>Eze 39:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=1'>Amo 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=7&verse=14'>Mic 7:14</a><br/><a href='S:Argob'>Argob</a>; <a href='S:Ashtaroth'>Ashtaroth</a>; <a href='S:Edrei'>Edrei</a>; <a href='S:Jair'>Jair</a>"}]}